{"tid":1373593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中》元朗「藤條車」搜出武士刀、公安帽   車主身分疑點重重更         有網友懷疑是中聯辦副部長「葉虎」","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T23:19:01.000Z","uid":35790,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b37af808d3dae2293892c180474534047a316d2c","tid":1373593,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"反送中》元朗「藤條車」搜出武士刀、公安帽 車主身分疑點重重<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-27<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港反送中「光復元朗」遊行今（27）晚傳出元朗西鐵站旁一輛自小客車後座被人發現放有6根「藤條」，引起遊行民眾不滿。隨後又爆出後車廂放有武士刀、鐵管、木棍以及疑似中國公安帽，經查後車主非華人，疑點重重。<br />\n<br />\n綜合港媒報導，香港「光復元朗」遊行晚間有眼尖民眾發現，路邊一台黑色自小客車後座放有至少6根「藤條」，與上週攻擊市民的白衣歹徒武器相同，引起群眾不滿，砸破車窗並留下「踢走黑社會」等標語。<br />\n<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨後又有憤怒民眾撬開其後車廂，竟發現內藏「武士刀」、「鐵管木棍」、以及疑似「中國公安帽」，消息傳出香港社群一片嘩然。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》指出，經查詢車牌後，車主全名為「Karunanayaka Mudiyanselage, Eranda M」，非華人但持有當地身分證，1999年2月3日首次註冊，地址為元朗八鄉錦莆路吳家村。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">據悉，現場民眾根據車中電費帳單，指出實際用車者可能為一位住在南邊圍村的「YIP FOO」（粵語音），更有網友懷疑這就是香港中聯辦新界工作部副部長「葉虎」。</span><br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"64e9ba9e970b969b86576340071ceb242b1b49b3","tid":1373593,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7e8b9cd07890a5eaef90f874310feaf2dd5660","tid":1373593,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"PUSH<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家入去填低感受</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經收左集超過二百人嘅感受，幫我地推到上一千、二千 OK ？</span></span><br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"40b90f00c85b23d01e48b74676c7764ad1303cc5","tid":1373593,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T00:53:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bec3f3ef2c21ec5a6d0ff652f8a73c533cb9b6d","tid":1373593,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:23:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"16229fb0daef2f761a0a3c320c4c0bbbd938d57c","tid":1373593,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:36:11.000Z","msg":"流動武器庫，匪犬快領功啦"},{"pid":"5dc98e986560d574b011219d95ffdc37a27a579d","tid":1373593,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:25:18.000Z","msg":"推撚爆條仆街賤狗葉虎既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e25c1c0a30b8f1ec4942ce2f44e7923244e41c","tid":1373593,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:27:02.000Z","msg":"幫台灣助攻！"},{"pid":"96d9044f1685ed97db9f57237a63a6f9dbaeed64","tid":1373593,"uid":281516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:27:42.000Z","msg":"［需共識］齊上齊落 vs 自主撤水（集中討論）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374867</a>"},{"pid":"1de70d8d458773237ecdb1c374a6e13076cd4cc3","tid":1373593,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:30:34.000Z","msg":"自由時辦<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜入過中聯辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705becad9f657eb3cd9b4b163bb7216ea4420688","tid":1373593,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自由時報<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜入過中聯辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"aac6b8854e5791847ad9657722fcfaa8879e5627","tid":1373593,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\